projects.title: Calculator App
projects.description: This is one of the most enjoyable applications I've built. I ran into a few issues with mathematical logic and spent quite a bit of time making sure that it works as expected even in the most complicated cases. In all I learned how to better interact with the DOM and utilize the debugging tools in Chrome.

projects.title: Star Wars App
projects.description: This was a tough application to complete. I spent quite a bit of time banging my head on the wall and ran into a few issues rendering the data from the API in a table. This project was vital in understanding how to interact with a RESTful API.
